criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  postmenopausal without hormone therapy replacement, if woman;

          -  present peripheral artery disease (ankle brachial index < 0.90) in one or both lower
             limbs;

          -  do not present neurological / cognitive diseases;

          -  is able to practice home-based exercise;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  patients will only be excluded if they make any medication changes before completing
             the intervention period or present any health problems that prevent physical activity.
